Please implement a proper storage abstraction layer to make it easy to test entirely in dev mode while being ready for production. The current PR mentions Firestore implementation but the actual storage layer isn't properly abstracted yet.

## Required Architecture

```
src/lib/storage/
├── index.ts              # Factory + getStorage()
├── interface.ts          # IStorageAdapter interface
├── adapters/
│   ├── mock.ts          # MockStorageAdapter (in-memory)
│   └── firestore.ts     # FirestoreStorageAdapter
```

## Implementation Requirements

